Dominique Nohain https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominique_Nohain 0 Dominique Nohain (8 July 1925 – 30 May 2017) was a French actor, dramatist, screenwriter and theatre director. He was the son of Jean Nohain and thus cousin with Jean-Claude Dauphin. Dominique_Nohain ( 8_July_1925 – 30_May_2017 ) was a_French_actor , dramatist_,_screenwriter_and_theatre_director .
